This is a Zen Desk

   It’s true that Zendesk was created to bring a sense of calm to the
   often chaotic world of customer service.

   It’s also true that Zendesk was born on a literal desk. Well, actually
   it was a door. And really,  it was more of a kitchen table. A lot of
   beer was spilled on it. Innocence was lost here, direction and purpose
   found.
   The original Zen Desk

Zendesk isn’t...

   Your mum’s
   favourite spa.

   A breeding farm
   for succulents.

   A very chill desk company.

   An alternative band.

